FinderBar New Tab extension is your easiest quick access to your last visited sites, right in the comfort of your web browser.

By clicking "Add to chrome", you accept and agree to installing FinderBar extension and setting Chrome New Tab search to that provided by the service.
You also agree to the 'End User License Agreement 'and the 'Privacy Policy'.

The search feature within the extension will be provided by Microsoft Bing. That said, the extension will not make any changes in your default browser search setting.
